title: Plackers Micro Mint Dental Flossers, Fresh Mint Flavor, Fold-Out Toothpick, Super Tuffloss, Easy Storage with Sure-Zip Seal, 150 Count
description: You've got smiles for miles. Keep it looking fresh with Plackers Micro Mint Flossers. Easily remove those bits of ick with smooth Super Tuffloss, engineered not to stretch, shred or break and a built-in fold-out toothpick that folds away after use. The easy grip handle provides more control and comfort while cleaning between your teeth and gums. Rely on Plackers to Get the Gunk Out. Enjoy fresh breath with delicious mint flavor that leaves your mouth with a fresh clean feeling. Perfect for on-the-go or at-home dental care with easy storage and consumer preferred zipper close. Includes 150 mint dental flossers. Smile Like Everyone's Watching.
